quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  19,77,"Mbega wabonye umwe mubahakanye amajambo yacu nukuvuga ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe narahawe amatungo n’ibibondo"
  19,78,"Mbega yaronse inkuru zitazwi, canke yaronse indagano ku Mana nyene imigisha myinshi ihagije"
  19,79,"Sivyo none, mu vy’ukuri turandika ivyo avuga vyose, kandi tuzo mwongereza ikiringo kirekire c’ibihano"
  19,80,"Tuzotorana muvyo avuga vyose,\tkandi azo kwishikana wenyene"
  19,81,Baragize izindi mana atari Imana y’ukuri kugira ngo babatere intege mukuba fasha
  19,82,"Oya! Bazohakana amasengesho yabo, kandi bazoba abatumvikana nabo"
  19,83,"Mbega\tntubona\tyuko\ttwarungitse\tamashetani\thejuru\tya\tbamwe batemera Imana y’ukuri baguma bakokeza kugira amabi"
  19,84,"Rero ntubatware ningoga na ningoga abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri kugira ngo bahanwe, mugabo\tduharura igitigiri c’imisi yabo"
  19,85,Umusi tuzo begeranya abatinya Imana yabo y’ukuri tubajana kwa nyene imigisha yuko ari abashitsi bayo
  19,86,"Hanyuma\ttuzoba\tsunika\tabantu\tbabi\tmumuriro\tudahera\twitiriwe Jahannamu mugihe bazoba bafise inyota y’amazi y’umurengera"
  19,87,"Ntabushobozi\tbazoba\tbafise\tbwugu\tsabirwa\tatari\tbamwe\tbafashe amasezerano ku Mana nyene imigisha n’impuhwe zihagije"
  19,88,"N’abahakanyi b’Imana bavuga bati:- nyene imigisha ihagije yarigiriye ikibondo"
  19,89,Ntankeka mwazanye ijambo rishavuza cane mukuvuga ibi vyose
  19,90,Mukuvuga yuko nyene imigisha ifise ikibondo
  19,91,Nkuko bivugira yuko nyene imigisha ihagije yoba ifise ikibondo
  19,92,Kandi ntibibaho kwa nyene imigisha ihagije yuko yoba ifise ikibondo
  19,93,"Nta\tn’umwe\tari\tmw’Ijuru\tno\tkw’Isi\tatari\tuko\tazoshika\tkwa\tnyene imigisha ihagije mugihe nawe ari umushumvyi wayo"
  19,94,Yabafashe nukuba harura bimwe bikwiye
  19,95,N’umwe muribo azoshikira Imana yiwe k’umusi w’imperuka ari wenyene